Aright. Change this server: “.DeathlypvpzCv2.2” To what ever your server name is. Heres an example “somescape_cache”. Then save, and compile. I am pretty sure you downloaded the cache, considering there was three different downloads on that link your posted. Open the cache, extract it to your “C:/” drive. Not in program files or anything, just in the “C:/” drive. Then rename the cache folder that you just extracted into your C drive, to whatever name you put in the signlink.java. So, the cache folder in my example would be “somescape_cache”. Then just run your client, it should work. Let me know how that goes or if you need more help, but I think thats detailed enough.
